The paper discusses communication protocols for IoT systems, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses fog and cloud computing integration, which falls under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY).
